Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Cease what you are\Ndoing and gaze at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop everything, save for\Nthe thrumming of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Theft. It is an\Nespecially sweet vice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,more elegant than vandalism
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,and more complex\Nthan simple robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,A beautiful blend of secrets\Nand crime and mischief and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Like dear Heathcliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I am defined by my\Nall-consuming passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Stealing is my greatest\Ncarnal pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,a pleasure for which\NI will risk my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.58,Main,,0,0,0,,a sexy prison from\Nwhich there is no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I this way?\NWho can know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the slave and\Nwho's the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Do divine eyes fall\Nupon me any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,or have the given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The rush of a theft\Nallows me to forget all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,and yet to distantly\Nremember all, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Run and speak not.\NHide and run not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,When you've found\Nme, punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,When you've punished\Nme, kill me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Little boy, there is nothing\Nleft to steal from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You have long been an\Nempty shell. Just as I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, if you would gaze at\Nme, cease what you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop everything save for the\Nthrumming of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It was such\Na tiny thing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Almost insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,If I'd just given it to them,\Nthey probably would have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,left me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It was so beautiful,\Nas if someone had scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,a handful of gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And among them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,there was one black gem that\Ngleamed the brightest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But what you were\Nprotecting was your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,"I will protect this, too,"\NI thought to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,This priceless gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,A necklace has been stolen-- an\Nheirloom of the Bourbone family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.03,Main,,0,0,0,,There were hundreds\Nof police guards on site,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,but it was stolen from\Nright under their noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko Mine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Last month it was a golden\Nring from Mycenaean Greece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's got a taste\Nfor the gaudier items lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, she's been taking\Na page from Lupin's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Woman doesn't know her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,This time it's the\NDuchess of l'Angoulée's tiara,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,housed at the Musée des\Nbeaux-arts de Marséne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been reassigned\Nto Fujiko Duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm on her case full time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:00.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hunt Lupin\N'til she's caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate wasting time on some\Nthird-rate female thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Even as we speak,\NLupin could b--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I will dedicate myself\Nto arresting Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,On my life, I'll get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this slop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The substance is called\N"oatmeal." I tried boiling it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.44,Main,,0,0,0,,in fish stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell is with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Nyou're my guardian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What's in this for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to sleep with me,\Nbe a man and say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Just get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, she is\Nan unapologetic seductress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,In the beginning I revered her\Nas something almost holy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Have my powers of\Nobservation been corrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.94,Main,,0,0,0,,A deadly flaw for one\Ndevoted to the path
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,of the sword but perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't wholly incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And now we bring you\Nbreaking news on the theft
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,of the Bourbone necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Investigators have released\Nthe name Fujiko Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.34,Main,,0,0,0,,as the party who had\Nallegedly given them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,advanced notes of the crime.\NThis comes to us via
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,press conference\Nheld only moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,This comes on the heels of the\NMycenaean ring theft last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a mystery,\Nthe woman called Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I must learn\Nthe truth about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It will give me a chance\Nto practice my swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Update, sir:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Security is airtight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I've stationed fifty\Nguards at the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,thirty at the back,\Nand another three hundred or so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,around the building's perimeter\Nand in the neighboring streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,An ant couldn't sneak in here,\Nlet alone a thieving rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Gas masks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Tear gas released\Nfrom the sprinklers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything is going\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold your ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Protect the tiara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector, perhaps Fujiko\Ndecided not to make her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Contact the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I want this authenticated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The perfect crime,\Npreceded by a written warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,The MO of this is much too\Nflashy for it to have been
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Unlike Lupin, who gets\Noff on the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,of stealing itself. Fujiko\Nonly has eyes for the loot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't go out\Nof her way to take risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.48,Main,,0,0,0,,There are four\Npossible points of entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,But none show any trace\Nof being forced which means
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,the tiara wasn't\Nstolen that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The reasonable assumption,\Nthen, is that it had already
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,swapped out with a fake.\NExcept that the museum had been
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,sealed off the whole week since\Nthe warning note was sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,We had the tiara analyzed\Ntwo days before the theft,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.59,Main,,0,0,0,,and it was the genuine article.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,And if that wasn't enough,\Nthe police have apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,discovered her hair and\Nfingerprints at each crime scene
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,as if she were deliberately\Nleaving clues behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,How transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What we've got here is-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A dirty cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,And that means-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,We've received\Nanother note from Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Her target this time is\NMarie Louise's engagement ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,which is housed at the\NMusée Archéologique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oscar, you swore on your life\Nthat you would get Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,In that case,\NI'll leave it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What will you do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:34.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Until this case is solved,\Nyou can't go after Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is the inspector\Nabandoning the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:45.60,Main,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Fujiko Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he trying\Nto capture Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,By now shouldn't\Nhe want her, dead or alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lieutenant Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko Mine isn't\Nwanted for murder yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That could change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, don't be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,We have a common interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,An owl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We've taken the liberty of\Nlooking into your background.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zenigata took you\Nin when you had no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,With his help, you clawed your\Nway to the rank of Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.71,Main,,0,0,0,,In time, the respect and\Nadmiration you felt for him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,evolved into love,\Nand then passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, you will\Neven kill for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you want him\Nto pursue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Why dress as Fujiko Mine then,\Nwhen disguising yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:14.03,Main,,0,0,0,,as Lupin would surely draw his\Nattention that much faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Just shut up, you stupid bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You want Inspector\NZenigata to "interrogate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.16,Main,,0,0,0,,you the same way\Nhe did Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The sharp, sweet\Nintimacy of that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,The deep,\Npenetrating questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We can help you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We can give you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We can make\Nyour dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Simply follow the path\Nuntil it leads you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,to The Bride of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko sent warning of\Na crime during this week's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Fete Nationale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,The festival centers on\N"the bride of the year,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,who symbolizes faithfulness\Nto the Revolution until death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujiko's stated target\Nis the gown worn by the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.18,Main,,0,0,0,,The dress is adorned with\Nprecious gems from all over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,the world, each more\Nbeautiful than the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The gown is lovely enough to\Noutshine the bride who wears it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be commanding\Nthis operation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.23,Main,,0,0,0,,in Inspector Zenigata's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Breaking news, the theft of\NMarie Louise's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,He acts all noble but in the\Nend, all men are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,...to Fujiko Mine. The suspect\Nis said to have shot an officer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:55.04,Main,,0,0,0,,to death before fleeing\Nthe scene with the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,In contrast to the theft\Nof Duchess l'Angoulee's tiara,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,this crime was\Nextremely brutal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.64,Main,,0,0,0,,A tiara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall adorn\Nyour head with a tiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...Growing frustration within\Nthe precinct and anger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,over the loss of one of\Ntheir own has prompted them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,to bring in reinforcements,\Nso the case can be resolved...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to kill Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Count Almeida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Excellent news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,A new page is about\Nto be written
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,in the tale of Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,One please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,A man cannot fight on\Nan empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.87,Main,,0,0,0,,A bomb threat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,The perp claims to have planted\Na bomb somewhere in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,How do we know this isn't a ploy\Nto distract our attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Celebrating the Fete Nationale\Nis an important part
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,of our culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't simply\Ncancel the parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What is Fujiko thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all, I would guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No way is this\NFujiko Mine's handiwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.27,Main,,0,0,0,,She would never pull\Na stunt like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Consider what\Nwe know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,About how she operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,This recent string\Nof crimes isn't her style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's far more likely that\Nsomebody else is behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But sir how could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of evidence\Nto place her at the--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe in what I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe what\NI can see-can see-can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe in Fujiko Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You believe in Fujiko Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,A parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,A hidden bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Vile, filthy spittoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,There are some things that\Ncan only truly be understood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,between a man and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Things that cannot be\Nfelt or realized until
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,the two have joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,We have not come here\Nto fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,We wish only a moment\Nof your time to speak about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,the plans for the parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't take much more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you already\Nmanipulated me enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What else do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Start chirping, you damn birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Attention: the Bride\Nis approaching point S
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The parade will proceed down\Nthe Avenue des Chandeliers and,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,finally, to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Just before it reaches\Na bridge, there will be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,a shower of fireworks.\NAt about the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,a bomb planted at the\Nbridge's center will detonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.94,Main,,0,0,0,,The bridge will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,As chaos ripples through the\Ncrowd and the police scramble
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,to control the situation,\Nyou will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:59.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You will whisk the Bride of\Nthe Revolution away to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Or so it will seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead, you will\Nseize her dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't get through to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Trouble on the parade route!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The road's been blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,A ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright let alter the route!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,We are the keepers\Nof this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The parade will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Again with the owls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta say, the guy\Nwho set this up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.03,Main,,0,0,0,,is one determined bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to disable\Nthe vibration-triggered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,detonator first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If the owl's talons so much as\Nbrush that stick, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we can immobilize\Nit with a little adhesive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a thief, not a bomb expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:38.35,Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't like people\Nwho pull this kind of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Please remain where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Good news, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been able to keep\Nthe parade going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot how\Nmany years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,How long it's been since\NI took a low-paying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,thankless job in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't take much time\Nfor corruption to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That was the only way for\Na guy like me to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,to the top or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But right here in this\Nspot I met a grubby kid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,who did whatever it took\Nto protect one measly franc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zenigata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I learned something from\Nthe little brat that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.64,Main,,0,0,0,,He taught me there's one thing\Nyou should never let go of,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter how dirty\Nyour hands are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It may seem like a trivial\Nlittle thing but it's all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,that a man's really got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You let it go\Nand you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything you've done\Nwill turn to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So I reported my superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost all chance of promotion\Nbut I don't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe in people who do what\Nit takes to protect their pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,A black gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I almost lost what\NI really cared about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.80,Main,,0,0,0,,by trying to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't give a damn\Nabout my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,There was something\Nelse I wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter how dirty I had to\Nget or how far I had to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Still armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.34,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no time to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, I held it\Nin my hand all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,As wretched as I am you\Nbelieved in me, all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That belief is all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's what I really\Nwant to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:13.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It's mine forever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.35,Main,,0,0,0,,My gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,My priceless black gem.
